Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a butterfly on a flower,{鼻か蝶々か蝶々か花か}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru decided to cross-dress{女に見舞う蘭丸は}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and came to support Benio, without knowing how she truly feels.{紅緒の気持ちも知らないで迷惑な応援}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this disguise could very well be unmasked,{だが男女のその正体がもしもバレたら一大}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact Shinobu, perhaps recognising Ranmaru,{少尉は蘭丸の正体を知ってか知らずか}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,mysteriously started giggling.{謎めいた微笑みを浮かべた}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the old and wise count's keen look managed to look through Ranmaru's cover,{亀の甲より年の功老伯爵の慧眼はらんまるの?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and things took a turn for the worse.{またまた迎えた大ピンチ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Benio used her force{されど?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and got to dispel all doubts. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter the bath with Benio and wash her back.{そなた一緒に入って紅男様のお背中を促しするのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we are, with troubles piling up one after another!{さもあらばあれ重ね重ねの大ピンチ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:06.00,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,300)\c&HF1E6E4&\pos(467.027,80)\bord0\blur1\fs60\b1}Episode 13\NLove is a sailboat of reflection
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was awfully close, Ranmaru.{酷い目に遭っちゃったわね蘭丸}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least they didn't discover my identity, don't you think?{でも正体がバレないでよかったね微妙さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!{ほんとね}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared for a moment.{さすがになってしまう焦っちゃったわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Lady Benio.{失礼しますべにお様}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Count would like you to make tea.{あの,御前様がお茶を一緒にいかがかとおっしゃってます}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, I'll go make it right now.{わかりました今行きます}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{行きましょう}Let's go,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I shall leave.{じゃあ僕はこれで}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Benio.{おやすみなさいbenioさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{ah, ranmaru, あんたの部屋は}Oh, Ranmaru, do you have a room now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, with only three maids living there.{メイドばっかり3人で人部屋なんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Three?{3人も}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you need to be extra careful to keep your cover.{じゃあ他の人たちに気づかれないようにしなくちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, don't worry,{平気平気}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just act as usual,{もうあとはいつもの通り}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll just sleep, after all.{眠るだけだもん}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, today went smoothly.{そうよね今日はもう大丈夫ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!{じゃあね}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, with his usual...{いつもの通りいつもの愛用の}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,flower-patterned loincloth!?{花柄の越中 - 越中 stands for 越中ふんどし, loincloth}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru! \NOh, never mind.{/ I let it slip/shouldn't be saying that}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko! Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.{りっぱ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, do you need help with something?{Benio様何かご用ですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it's nothing important.{あいや別に大したようでは}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you can let us seniors take care of Ranko.{では蘭子さんのことは先輩の私たちにお任せください}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you.{お・お願いいたします}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she kind of panicked?{では慌ててんのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat some grilled chicken...{つくねの焼き鳥食べたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.{よいしょっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pads aren't suitable for people who turn while asleep.{寝相の悪い人間にはパッドと向いてないわね - not too sure about that peddo/petto/patto}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Ranmaru tosses while sleeping.{ranmaruって寝相がいいかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought!{やっぱり}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ranmaru, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master...\NYoung Master...{若様若様}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to my room, okay?{私の家へ越すのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, why?{えどうして}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think they won't notice that?{それがみんなにバレずに済むと思うの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.{了解}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move your things tomorrow morning.{荷物は明日の朝取りに来ればいいわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting to sleep in the same room as Benio...{紅緒さんと一緒の部屋に寝られるなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so happy!{僕嬉しい}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too excited!{?んじゃないの - kinda guessing}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I will sleep here and you will sleep there.{こっちは私の?,そっちはらんまるの?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? If you cross the border, I won't let it slide!{わかってんのねこれを超えたら承知しないわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight then, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so bright...{眩しいなぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm ready.{どっこいしょった}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, are you awake yet?{紅緒さんそろそろ起きない}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you were here, Lady Benio.{ああべにおさまこんなところに}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko, what's the deal with that face of yours?{rankoどうしたのそんな顔して}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio used to be such a late riser,{あの朝寝坊の紅緒さんが}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this is happening.{僕信じられないな}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, what is it you're doing here?{benio様何をしてるのですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing... Can't you tell? I'm sweeping.{何よって見ればわかるでしょお掃除よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Masters should not be doing this kind of work!{そんなことを若奥様の見習いがすべきことじゃありません}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you have maids otherwise?{何のために私たちメイドがいるんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am learning to become a good homemaker,{でも(おおせ?)の方向に(乗せる)ことも - not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so I need to make some practise.{一通りは経験しなければいけないんですで}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, who gave that order?{誰がそんな命令を}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Mrs. Kisaragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, it's always that hag!{えっ覚えといてあの(古着?)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like she's making me do this out of spite,{でも別に意地悪してるわけじゃないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that woman is just devoted to her duties.{あの人は職務に忠実なだけよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll just give her hell!{いいえあいつ血祭りにあげてやるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be so rude.{物騒なこと言わないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't making a mess of this place{そのうちをしっちゃかめっちゃかにするの}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,your initial goal here?{benioさんの目的じゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!{おはようございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone.{おはよう皆さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.{良いできですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who arranged this flower?{この花は誰がいけました}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?{誰がいけたのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, I...{あの私が}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be, it is not your style at all.{いいえ紅緒様のはずはございません}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to say that I had Ranmaru arrange this.{ですから私が言いつけて蘭子がいけました}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it all by yourself?{全てrankoがいけたのですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an excellent job.{出来栄えは見事です}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just did what I could.{まぁざっとこんなもんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you did something unnecessary!{しかし余計なことをしてくれましたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't do it for Lady Benio, or she'll never learn!{紅緒様に生けていただかねば修行になりませぬ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, don't do unwanted things!{明朝からは余計なことに手出し無用}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!?{わかりましたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm to blame as I was the one giving Ranko the order.{rankoに頼んだ私がいけなかったのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's my fault because I accepted.{いいえお手伝いをした私が悪いのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You two must know your own places.{お二人ともそれぞれの立場をわきまえなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?{わかりましたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some lint on your clothes.{kisaragi様のお召し物に糸くずが}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, I cut it, sorry for troubling you.{取れましたどうも引き止めいたしまして}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.{ご苦労}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0\b1\u0}What is that!?{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so careless!{私としたことが}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is disgraceful!{という醜態を}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you'll learn how to write haiku.{本日は俳句を学んでいただきます}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,By mixing quiet and simplicity, you can even reach the zen.{わびとサビこれぞまさしく禅の境地にも等しく}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the essence of haiku.{俳句の真髄でございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a poem by Matsuo Basho.{芭蕉の(おきな?)も読みました}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Frogs jumped in an old pond and it splashed.{古池や蛙飛びこむ水の音}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a well-known haiku.{ここも通じての名句でございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Go towards her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For this reason...{でありますからして}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand frogs!{気持ちが悪い}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a haiku too.{私も一句読めましたわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The old hag jumped in an old pond, splashing all over,{古池やばばあ飛び込む水しぶきたかし}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a hypermeter.{字余り}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I am dressed like a girl,{いくら女形の修業をつんだりといえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I still need to meet my physical needs.{こう女の格好ばかりってのは答えるのは全く}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily there's no one around, so let's do it!{幸いあたりに人影もないしやってしまい}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be men's heaven.{これぞ男の快感おわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi, you look ghastly!{kisaragiさん、お顔真っ青}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you too tired?{お疲れが出たんですわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She is pi—{tachishou - piss on the go/in a man's fashion/while standing}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In these cases, you need some therapy.{そういう時はちょっと指圧など- Ugh that skull cracking made me feel bad}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain this Ranko maid was taking a man's piss.{確かにあの蘭子と有名と太刀}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too disgusting, it can't be real.\NI need to collect myself.{まさか、そんなおぞましい. 冷静にならねば}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Benio came here, I've been feeling more and more worn out.{ともかくbenio様が来てからというもの少々疲れ気味なのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My wonderful roses,{わしの自慢のバラが}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it looks like they've fully bloomed.{端正の会やって見事に咲いたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that place is...{はやく、そ・その場所は}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, stay away!{殿様いけません}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I stay away?{何がいかんのじゃそれが}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was... man's piss! Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been quite weird recently.{お前この頃少しおかしいぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should see a doctor!{医者にでも見てもらい}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm completely fine.{いやそんなとんでもございません}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a fine smell!{いい匂い}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful...{これあかんね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, aren't you overdoing it a little?{ranmaru少しやりすぎよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I just listened to my nature calls.{自然の呼び声に応えただけだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Boss?{どうしたんです親分?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing special,{それにしても}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but Ranmaru needs to learn some basic etiquette.{最低のエチケットってものは守ってもらわなくちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, aren't you acting strange?{微妙さんそれおかしいんじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We are doing all of this{僕たちがここにこうしているのは}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to break your engagement as soon as possible, right?{1日も早くバカげた縁談をご破算にするためでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right, don't you think so, Boss?{そうそうそうじゃないんですかよ親分}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{まあな}Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we need to be as wild as we can{だったら派手に暴れて}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll be kicked out in no time.{1日も早く追い出されましょうよ} 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah! Boss, to be honest, I can't wait to raise hell!{ええねあしも実は腕はムズムズしてるんですよ親分}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.{ほら見て}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best time to execute our plan.{そろそろここを引き上げる潮時じゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the time has come.{来るべき時が来たようね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Is there anything you want to do to go out in style?{そうよお別れ工業に一丁派手にやらかしますか}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if this is the case, I should.{そうねこうなったら破れかぶれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo! Let's make a mess of this place!{ほいったババンドやりましょうぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! I can always count on you, Ushi!{賛成牛さんて頼もしいわー}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu... so this is goodbye.{少尉。。。よいお別れで}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? That sound...{あの音は}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:16.89,Sign,,0,0,0,,Boss Hanamura Benio's Dwelling{花村紅緒親分御宿所}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'm done.{よーしできたこれでよーし}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you come up with this time?{お前はまた何を始めたんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? It's a signboard, a signboard, just look!{何ってよ看板だよ看板見りゃ分かるだろうかよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all of this for?{なんということを}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,By doing this, the whole world will know that Boss lives here!{こうやっときゃ世間様にうちの親分ここにいるってすぐにわからあな}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't the only one!{これだけじゃないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme, lemme show you. Here!{ほら所}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are to be nailed on doorways, too{/in front of rooms}{これが部屋の前に貼るやつ}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,Boss Hanamura Benio's Bed{/Sleeping}room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These are for bathrooms.{これが便所の前のやつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.31,Sign,,0,0,0,,Boss Hanamura Benio's Toilet{/Restroom}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You, unruly man...{lit is "the man of your name" so I'm half-guessing}{お前と言う男はいやー}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Just kidding, kidding!{いや冗談冗談}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi, I like your style, I really do!{kisaragiさんスタイルいいね本当よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!{黙れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away immediately!{とっとと立ち去りなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you're so scary!{いや怖い怖い}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Making a fool of me!{己,人をバカにして}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll chop your head off!{その首をギザギザにしてやる}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,666,,Time to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait, wait! Ah, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:13.89,Default,,0,0,666,,Stop there! Take this, this, this! You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss always tell me it's so funny to kid you!{あのばあさんからかうと面白いって親分がいうからよ - not sure about the translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare...{/shut that mouth}{己}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't wait at all!{待てません}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, {この己待って}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,insolent!{己}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw-aw-aw-aw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell! \NThere's no stopping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd it come to this?{どうなってんの}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my,{おや}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisaragi, what in the world happened?{如月どうしましたか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are bloodshot, what's wrong?{目を血走らせて何かあったのですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just that...{いやそれがその}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! What you need that for?{もう何ですかそれは}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, for no particular reason.{いいえ何でもありません}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel a little exhausted, Kisaragi?{少し疲れてるのではありませんかkisaragi}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...{いいえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Benio came here,{紅緒さんがいらしてから}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so many things have changed, so don't strain yourself.{この屋敷の雰囲気も変わってきたので無理ありませんが}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Something this trifling doesn't bother me,{これしきのことでまいるきさらぎではございません}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio's education is proceeding steadily.{benio様の教育も着々と進んでおりますれば}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's all good, then.{そうそれならよろしいのですが}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, these must be Tenmaru and Chimaru,{あれって今のは確かにtenmaruとchimaru}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're in our garden.{それもうちの中で}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What was happening in the corridor?{なんでしょう今何かおろうかを}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm...{あの}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These days my eyesight is rather poor,{私は目が悪いのでわかりませんが}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,what did that seem like?{そなたはどうです}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master's dogs are pulling the rickshaw!{お犬が！若様のお犬が人力車に！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisaragi! Hold yourself together! Kisaragi? Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.{なるほどなるほど}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mind is fatigued,{脳が腐れておる}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, she's definitely tired,{さよう完全に腐れておりますが}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,she needs to rest for the time being.{当分安静が必要ですぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she really make it out okay?{本当に大丈夫かしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,666,,I'm so worried!{心配だわー}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.\NThen, take care.{はいそれではお大事に}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We finished that hag off!{ついあのばあさんやっつけた}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're at it, we can go home, Benio!{これでもうじきうちに帰れるよねbenioさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home...{うちに}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I could do it...{そうね帰れる}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Going home...{うちに帰る}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If I return home...{うちに帰れば}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't see Shinobu's face anymore...{もう少尉の顔を見なくても住む}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If I return home...{うちに帰れば}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,there won't be any relationship between us anymore.{もう私と少尉とは何の関係もない}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be strangers...{赤の他人}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so lonely...{寂しいな}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it!\NIt's too late now.{バカな何を今更}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here with this goal in mind!{元々その木で来たのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...{まさか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, Benio...{まさか紅緒さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek! Who is it!?{いや誰じゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come in! Just don't!{ならぬならぬ！入ってはならぬ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kisaragi, it's me.{如月さん僕だよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi, I heard you collapsed.{Kisaragiさん倒れたんだって}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it's nothing important.{ なんでもありませんこれしきなこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being in such a bad shape.{お見苦しいところを目にかけまして}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't overdo it, you are{無理をしてはいけないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,my irreplaceable nanny, after all,{/elderly maid/maid supervisor}{I think the trivia here is, baaya can be both a formal role, which I think is implied by shinobu, which is "master housekeeper" and a very intimate to one person, a wet nanny, which is rather what baaya is to Benio - pere}{僕には大切なバーやなんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to take care of yourself.{十分注意しなくちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, you're such a kind person...{若様もったいないおこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to take breaks sometimes,{たまにはゆっくりと休むといいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mrs. Kisaragi is to Shinobu{あのkisaragiさんは少尉にとっては}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,what my Nanny was to me?{私のばあやと同じような人だったのね}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we really went a bit too far.{少しやりすぎだったかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is your tea.{お茶をお持ちしました}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.{失礼します}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, your pads are all over your back.{蘭丸くんパットが縦に並んで背中に来ているよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody may have figured your play out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dead sure! He called me Ranmaru, after all!{確かに蘭丸って呼んだんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected!{やっぱり}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But why didn't he tell everyone yet?{でもどうしてみんなに話さないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew that I've been with you from the start{この私が男の蘭丸としじゅう一緒にいて}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I slept with you in the same room too.{いつも同じ部屋で寝起きしているっていうのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it, he knew that Ranmaru loves me, not to mention what I risked.{ranmaruは私を愛していて私はすごく危険な目に遭わないとも限らないのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was never worried...{それを心配していないのは}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough,{やっぱり}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,he does not care about me at all.{私のことなんか何とも思ってないから}
