Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the almighty High Collar Lady{剣を取らせりゃ天下無敵のハイカラさんも}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is now lost in thought{今じゃほのかに}
