Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.95,0:22:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to understand Shinobu's feelings,{少尉の心の底を測りかねて}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:22:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,our worried High Collar Lady{思い悩むはいからさんに}
